title: Jay Z destroyed the words "Medium Toes of God" in Hillary Clinton Raleigh.
subtitle: The social media rumor on election night is that the guest artist Jay Z sang the words "Medium finger to God, no fist, I'm president" at the Hillary Clinton rally.
author: David Emery
vclaim: Jay-Z sang the words "Medium Finger to God, Fist on you, I'm a boss" at the Hillary Clinton rally.
